[
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.1",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 1,
    "text": "These {are} the sons of Israel; Reuben, Simeon, Levi, and Judah, Issachar, and Zebulun, {Israel: or, Jacob}",
    "hash": "f02589353fb72cce2dce371781d5276b53a6b0d369c0771a905719ac0a579b3b"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.2",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 2,
    "text": "Dan, Joseph, and Benjamin, Naphtali, Gad, and Asher.",
    "hash": "cc1019e1f561b87f879413747524b6a5bdf8141e90c7ab3a439e6015931b5797"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.3",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 3,
    "text": "The sons of Judah; Er, and Onan, and Shelah: {which} three were born unto him of the daughter of Shua the Canaanitess. And Er, the firstborn of Judah, was evil in the sight of the LORD; and he slew him.",
    "hash": "9b5196817869aa7def82ea31dc14731cb4db8f2dfbbb4a3a0e3b25d8e5fd185d"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.4",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 4,
    "text": "And Tamar his daughter in law bare him Pharez and Zerah. All the sons of Judah {were} five.",
    "hash": "c6aa58639228cbe612cd8047c405b5eacdec52a1dc1d420c85f818f6e4aed429"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.5",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 5,
    "text": "The sons of Pharez; Hezron, and Hamul.",
    "hash": "e7f66480ff86bd8f2e2988ae0c5862bb879926bf083bae3075b9661dc22142e4"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.6",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 6,
    "text": "And the sons of Zerah; Zimri, and Ethan, and Heman, and Calcol, and Dara: five of them in all. {Zimri: or, Zabdi} {Dara: or, Darda}",
    "hash": "63d270c44af4a851a84a164e4a7110f1d7556d0c8c50204116e3508b5da17405"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.7",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 7,
    "text": "And the sons of Carmi; Achar, the troubler of Israel, who transgressed in the thing accursed. {Achar: or, Achan}",
    "hash": "1424b0cb3f358c12f9005868ab71b81399b24beb71601e3a6e31a36b97396274"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.8",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 8,
    "text": "And the sons of Ethan; Azariah.",
    "hash": "843d4957cbfca856b7984720f380b16ba16b525ab2ae1e6996c8a11c2a347450"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.9",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 9,
    "text": "The sons also of Hezron, that were born unto him; Jerahmeel, and Ram, and Chelubai. {Ram: Gr. Aram} {Chelubai: or, Caleb}",
    "hash": "a73c4e129391d105560d7e61088f8a3fc3344051d6e32d6efa624bdffb0e4f47"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.10",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 10,
    "text": "And Ram begat Amminadab; and Amminadab begat Nahshon, prince of the children of Judah;",
    "hash": "de7d4fbb2583c58d9bb6e2cd2626ebe232474975099adcb6b9585e1d87f36888"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.11",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 11,
    "text": "And Nahshon begat Salma, and Salma begat Boaz, {Salma: also called, Salmon}",
    "hash": "7a84dbd352ce0b440ea6d332099b058f7e85e1989897ace8ff47d1558de44740"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.12",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 12,
    "text": "And Boaz begat Obed, and Obed begat Jesse,",
    "hash": "7688eb4be8f92ecc525a66f4d3fa6d137ad89c4dc7519a81f92a6dc6c236113b"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.13",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 13,
    "text": "And Jesse begat his firstborn Eliab, and Abinadab the second, and Shimma the third, {Shimma: or, Shammah}",
    "hash": "f4b5d69cef1d73f4eb328ecb71cd108528f9d3189ac2a1fb478e5e78fe094d14"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.14",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 14,
    "text": "Nethaneel the fourth, Raddai the fifth,",
    "hash": "f0b53b591f2246e98cbd2c763aeb2643c1d84a462fbbb7556397215eeb008fa2"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.15",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 15,
    "text": "Ozem the sixth, David the seventh:",
    "hash": "41d813254d9dc668bb0a59bf47de73ef3726bfb982ed5975764c18bfa0d36dbd"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.16",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 16,
    "text": "Whose sisters {were} Zeruiah, and Abigail. And the sons of Zeruiah; Abishai, and Joab, and Asahel, three.",
    "hash": "0362efe5f3e5627e3f445ae04b3d641a3eb84fe22b91825b7c9d70421a1ffaf2"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.17",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 17,
    "text": "And Abigail bare Amasa: and the father of Amasa {was} Jether the Ishmeelite. {Jether...: also called, Ithra an Israelite}",
    "hash": "e8e6f17b0e2909a307d8fb3d740c485b422e686516eadb83ce72fce077220d9c"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.18",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 18,
    "text": "And Caleb the son of Hezron begat {children} of Azubah {his} wife, and of Jerioth: her sons {are} these; Jesher, and Shobab, and Ardon.",
    "hash": "7337cad1337faac9889301457e11404dfae975e28e558a86a208c1933c2f354c"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.19",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 19,
    "text": "And when Azubah was dead, Caleb took unto him Ephrath, which bare him Hur.",
    "hash": "1f42a0d56dddb8b3daff0754f1c0253b845bdb7ab103bbf952d86be5cec46fb7"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.20",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 20,
    "text": "And Hur begat Uri, and Uri begat Bezaleel.",
    "hash": "7aa3204b1913386ba7a525ac92635921c4297ddf49c62f89b70a67d7b85d7721"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.21",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 21,
    "text": "And afterward Hezron went in to the daughter of Machir the father of Gilead, whom he married when he {was} threescore years old; and she bare him Segub. {married: Heb. took}",
    "hash": "f94d3667f1769a1ec16949da6c95794f1b5076cd30f772d0746efc8771616f03"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.22",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 22,
    "text": "And Segub begat Jair, who had three and twenty cities in the land of Gilead.",
    "hash": "0ffcafc4c61fd7e0e3aa96fc86895e7a537d089d24d9c1511e53867388bb0209"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.23",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 23,
    "text": "And he took Geshur, and Aram, with the towns of Jair, from them, with Kenath, and the towns thereof, {even} threescore cities. All these {belonged to} the sons of Machir the father of Gilead.",
    "hash": "c13b23c8b7816e7f7fb9a4b5e4fda1da839790b7e3134ff349c9bb5ded2b52cc"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.24",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 24,
    "text": "And after that Hezron was dead in Calebephratah, then Abiah Hezron's wife bare him Ashur the father of Tekoa.",
    "hash": "2a51383cc4832cc5827f8576643ebbfd12bf0ece3161a3bd8d64bd66e61f2711"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.25",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 25,
    "text": "And the sons of Jerahmeel the firstborn of Hezron were, Ram the firstborn, and Bunah, and Oren, and Ozem, {and} Ahijah.",
    "hash": "68a4f0c8850361cede17a4be9ba9df4da2adcb5e1875983233ef5a5901463e74"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.26",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 26,
    "text": "Jerahmeel had also another wife, whose name {was} Atarah; she {was} the mother of Onam.",
    "hash": "1aba7adcb54c291e502a1fd1ebd9419435de2e350bbbe9795ffb930fa8f031bd"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.27",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 27,
    "text": "And the sons of Ram the firstborn of Jerahmeel were, Maaz, and Jamin, and Eker.",
    "hash": "e8654df2e316aa153959c47c08c3387487946a9ce0c33a72a6231ef218447c69"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.28",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 28,
    "text": "And the sons of Onam were, Shammai, and Jada. And the sons of Shammai; Nadab, and Abishur.",
    "hash": "652b59e4f78a6da66f49c6e5e2c734762003bc2ddb1f9b1dfd7e45e4eecc6bcd"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.29",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 29,
    "text": "And the name of the wife of Abishur {was} Abihail, and she bare him Ahban, and Molid.",
    "hash": "151f694750e6ac8b4d2d6c6ba66c586924bb760f870f2a3434f0a9889a6e0cdf"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.30",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 30,
    "text": "And the sons of Nadab; Seled, and Appaim: but Seled died without children.",
    "hash": "324030815c12a22ee1c3dc5efad1310bca4bfc89a4b65b62573c9c318b6fb222"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.31",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 31,
    "text": "And the sons of Appaim; Ishi. And the sons of Ishi; Sheshan. And the children of Sheshan; Ahlai.",
    "hash": "5ef981c624bc2c1831a06154e66c3754c958a8f6083133853bfa85ffc973e36e"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.32",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 32,
    "text": "And the sons of Jada the brother of Shammai; Jether, and Jonathan: and Jether died without children.",
    "hash": "72f402634a830c2045b07b89d866d6552304f6d1f343245effdc308fffd2f0c7"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.33",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 33,
    "text": "And the sons of Jonathan; Peleth, and Zaza. These were the sons of Jerahmeel.",
    "hash": "fdbb9b3246ee033fbe7a406db284cc0cf58e87101f206b90ea8c8c7e44a7d3a0"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.34",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 34,
    "text": "Now Sheshan had no sons, but daughters. And Sheshan had a servant, an Egyptian, whose name {was} Jarha.",
    "hash": "dc5db58e69ab7f3114192d15a6fc7bef4cd91f8b139e96b4b6f1cff25080be35"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.35",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 35,
    "text": "And Sheshan gave his daughter to Jarha his servant to wife; and she bare him Attai.",
    "hash": "44cc12ce1ba162a1f887bc860702f951c7e0fb4520536ee126981405eef446ea"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.36",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 36,
    "text": "And Attai begat Nathan, and Nathan begat Zabad,",
    "hash": "3a755979449432feed467322f0c993174c45b4a1fba4c0e01b68b4aed6e62b7b"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.37",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 37,
    "text": "And Zabad begat Ephlal, and Ephlal begat Obed,",
    "hash": "be3065d7f6aead1d164c4dbc58c7b50a736786b7ade3fca0c35800925af72a7e"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.38",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 38,
    "text": "And Obed begat Jehu, and Jehu begat Azariah,",
    "hash": "307a4e44b7b31c36e529f6b50ad8ad8d4aba9c240853c7eb8b7a8470f206f468"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.39",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 39,
    "text": "And Azariah begat Helez, and Helez begat Eleasah,",
    "hash": "b0b99eb858e4eaed05e2d7da4846b25645d9f354338677bbd07f6489e595be56"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.40",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 40,
    "text": "And Eleasah begat Sisamai, and Sisamai begat Shallum,",
    "hash": "a2d9f774f92d12e6dd5f096d5d46d78fdeeef8501132617b240b08474751ebd0"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.41",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 41,
    "text": "And Shallum begat Jekamiah, and Jekamiah begat Elishama.",
    "hash": "d9bb7c05a60c8b0a53865f524fba6e93b8b6507b1b45f4dd4574e0cd9d8a385d"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.42",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 42,
    "text": "Now the sons of Caleb the brother of Jerahmeel {were}, Mesha his firstborn, which was the father of Ziph; and the sons of Mareshah the father of Hebron.",
    "hash": "d0a86da59c0157ed5a25e21a5ef5bab5f432a8d97d87171d7b918c4057400cb7"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.43",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 43,
    "text": "And the sons of Hebron; Korah, and Tappuah, and Rekem, and Shema.",
    "hash": "2ed0e23d6c6376fbb22c00ae13546ce5f8c9c22d02420489d25f21eaefcd5ddd"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.44",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 44,
    "text": "And Shema begat Raham, the father of Jorkoam: and Rekem begat Shammai.",
    "hash": "08c28004ac9dafdd682dec24098169433d59762dbf4280ef4091719eda2b5704"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.45",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 45,
    "text": "And the son of Shammai {was} Maon: and Maon {was} the father of Bethzur.",
    "hash": "11ae7647b77aa694611c2e5361c647314c231760a2aa732fc98ece52a6d9a949"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.46",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 46,
    "text": "And Ephah, Caleb's concubine, bare Haran, and Moza, and Gazez: and Haran begat Gazez.",
    "hash": "5f730b6761d51080117038626652ff00a505235a850bebfb97a0e3ec35492e3f"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.47",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 47,
    "text": "And the sons of Jahdai; Regem, and Jotham, and Geshan, and Pelet, and Ephah, and Shaaph.",
    "hash": "e524763431c4f9e94bb013fdefa41c57d5d2c59299f86c6bb11aeecd036c67f2"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.48",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 48,
    "text": "Maachah, Caleb's concubine, bare Sheber, and Tirhanah.",
    "hash": "7ac7eda49e40fc4ef00e5c903f4376ccea1590c43b64529f4e6742ba4088ca16"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.49",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 49,
    "text": "She bare also Shaaph the father of Madmannah, Sheva the father of Machbenah, and the father of Gibea: and the daughter of Caleb {was} Achsah.",
    "hash": "3ab4ea4fa3c0e5998f1819c2664be44640ee673cf355dc99290a68926e6905ad"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.50",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 50,
    "text": "These were the sons of Caleb the son of Hur, the firstborn of Ephratah; Shobal the father of Kirjathjearim, {Ephratah: also called, Ephreth}",
    "hash": "8e3745ff5e76584f40d1eb3295ca9f658fa0179ec3c6479ba17ca24837c57949"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.51",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 51,
    "text": "Salma the father of Bethlehem, Hareph the father of Bethgader.",
    "hash": "ea8ffb2607c063398fa9197d1ee6032d34c892d1e61e1e3463bf954519475604"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.52",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 52,
    "text": "And Shobal the father of Kirjathjearim had sons; Haroeh, {and} half of the Manahethites. {Haroeh: or, Reaiah} {half...: or, half of the Menuchites, or, Hatsihammenuchoth}",
    "hash": "f524f08c2b42a71bcb19961c91ec90e2d484110de1cf190f36331b20e6fe31ab"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.2.53",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 53,
    "text": "And the families of Kirjathjearim; the Ithrites, and the Puhites, and the Shumathites, and the Mishraites; of them came the Zareathites, and the Eshtaulites.",
    "hash": "453ef928e30ddd308da26e384f4a2b3e5cc5ed906f2f61b95a5c3316d18cbddc"
  },
